h4. +Summary+
Currently whenever a Confluence user updates his Profile picture, this info is visible in the Activity Stream in JIRA for every JIRA user. In many cases this kind of info is not relevant and JIRA admins do not want every JIRA user to be aware of it.

h4. +Suggestion+
There should be a Confluence filter in Activity Stream gadget that excludes all Profile Picture update events e.g.:
{code}Activity  -  is not  -  Profile Picture Updated{code}

